snippet.title: Anarch | Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a trailer for my public domain Doom-like game Anarch. The game is very special, extremely small, suckless, with tiny hardware demands, running
basically on any platforms. It has many nice properties and is one of its kind. It is completely free, both as in gratis and freedom. To get it, visit
https://drummyfish.gitlab.io/anarch/.
